> some way-out-of-the-money call options on Bed Bath in February and March,=
=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28907528.268=
558/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg4NjE1OC8wMDAxMTk=
