 trivial technical reasons, which got his retail-investor fans excited and =
pushed up the stock, and</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Cohen <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28907528.268558/aHR0c=
HM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg4NjE1OC8wMDAwOTIxODk1MjIw=
