-color: #ccc;"> disclosed</a>=C2=A0that actually he had dumped all of his s=
tock (and options).</li>
</ul>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Cohen took advantage of the rally to sell all =
his stock at an average price of about $23 per share. Bed Bath &amp; Beyond=
 did not. Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
28907528.268558/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg4NjE=
1OC8wMDAxMTkzMTI1MjIyMzQ2MTYvZDI4OTcwNmQ0MjRiNS5odG0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a2=
3cB3d8f658c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;"> the prospectus</a>=C2=A0that it filed today for its a=
t-the-market offering of up to 12 million shares. Here is <a href=3D"https:=
//link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28907528.268558/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2V=
