coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> its announcem=
ent</a> of =E2=80=9Cstrategic changes=E2=80=9D (store closures, new financi=
ng, etc.), and the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/28907528.268558/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg4Nj=
E1OC8wMDAxMTkzMTI1MjIyMzQ2MDMvZDI3OTAxM2RleDk5Mi5odG0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a=
