burn. She was ordered to sell the property and return the remaining funds o=
r face potential contempt of court charges. The case will return to court i=
n October.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I=E2=80=99m sorry but if I were the judge in t=
his case I=E2=80=99d order them to send her another $10.5 million. Teach th=
em a lesson. You=E2=80=99re a crypto exchange! Your refund mechanics consis=
t of a customer-service employee typing amounts in a box with no checks! Yo=
u threw away $10 million and didn=E2=80=99t notice it for months! Then you =
went to court to reverse your own mistake! Come on.=C2=A0</p>
